# CODEOWNERS - Automatic review requests for PRs
#
# This file defines code ownership for the finbot repository.
# When a PR modifies files in these directories, the specified owners
# will automatically be requested for review.
#
# Syntax: path/to/directory @github-username
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

